<h3 id="toc8"><span><span style="font-family: 'Nanum Brush Script', cursive; color: #390000; font-size: 150%">If I am Gone</span></span></h3>
<p>In the event that I have disappeared off of the wiki and IRC for a period longer than 6 months without any notice or updates, I entrust the curation of all my solo <em>La Rue Macabre</em> content to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609271581" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;">plaidypus</a></span>, all my other solo stuff to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609271581" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>, and my collaborative articles with their respective co-authors.</p>
<p>These curators are expressly allowed to make substantive modifications to my work, provided it doesn't change the overall theme of the piece. (An Alagaddan skip will remain Alaggadan, etc.)</p>
